  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Compare severe (acute and late) toxicity (Grade 3-5) caused by cetuximab and radiotherapy to that caused by cisplatin and radiotherapy.</measure>
    <time_frame>Up to two years after end of treatment.</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
